snippet.title: Pixels With Comics Trailer
snippet.description:
First trailer of Pixels With Comics is up!!!!!

Pixels With Comics is a 2d, Bullethell, Musical game, with combined of beautiful music with each concept and level that makes you always full energic with gameplay.


For contact: maziaryaghoubi@gmail.com
